{"tid":708301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果巴絲有唔開心，可以同我地入黎傾下","createTime":"2018-06-19T08:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T15:22:42.000Z","uid":122099,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"01cc5be0c6150ebdd98c50b736fb97ac1bc299e4","tid":708301,"uid":122099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:20:26.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇左個女仔濕疹新聞同有關post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d心 up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nr.i.p. 個女仔<br />\n同時希望各位巴絲以後見到呢d post<br />\n可以入去了解同安慰下當事人<br />\n而唔好鼓勵結束生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完個新聞之後<br />\n我係度諗我可以做d咩幫到類似既情況唔好再出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我決定左開呢個post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲有唔開心，可以入黎可以同我地傾下<br />\n係post 留言又好<br />\nTg 搵我都好<br />\n我都會盡量覆<br />\n另外有心既巴絲都可以係下面留低tg <br />\n一齊幫下d巴絲渡過唔開心時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我Tg: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/behopefulll\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbehopefulll&d=kfGbL%2FOjNJwp4oeQaGZtPwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d5a37612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/behopefulll</a><br />\n<br />\n我係一個普通絲打，希望可以有多d巴絲一齊幫下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTo: 唔開心既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n我係一個普通絲打，平凡人，<br />\n唔係咩社工，<br />\n一個普通打工仔，<br />\n但我都經歷過唔開心既階段，<br />\n明白可能有d唔開心未必想同相識既人講。<br />\n如果係咁，不妨可以同我/呢度既巴絲講<br />\n有我地陪住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nYou never walk alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e53419c2ac24ef489b939984324c64015bed17","tid":708301,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:22:01.000Z","msg":"不至尋死但幫推"},{"pid":"2ad9d6ec756e9fb8d1e0bd6ecdddf12a38efa6a1","tid":708301,"uid":7915,"like":0,"disl